name: CaseTeamMember
description: Represents a member of a case team.
summary: The {CaseTeamMember} object in the Salesforce application represents a team member assigned to a case. It has attributes including Id, ParentId (reference to parent object), MemberId (reference to team member), TeamTemplateMemberId (reference to team template member), TeamRoleId (reference to team role), TeamTemplateId (reference to team template), CreatedDate, CreatedById (reference to creator), LastModifiedDate, LastModifiedById (reference to last modifier), and SystemModstamp (datetime of last system modification).
label: Case Team Member
